ms-keyframes @name { @frames();}\r\n         @-o-keyframes @name { @frames(); }\r\n            @keyframes @name { @frames(); }\r\n}\r\n\r\n@sub-nav-heigth: 41px;\r\n\r\n.fadeLoop(@counter) when (@counter < 16 ) {\r\n    @fadeOutUpName: e(\"fadeOutUp@{counter}\");\r\n    @fadeInDownName: e(\"fadeInDown@{counter}\");\r\n\r\n    .keyframes(@fadeOutUpName, {\r\n        from { height: @sub-nav-heigth * @counter; }\r\n        to { height: 0;}\r\n    });\r\n\r\n    .keyframes(@fadeInDownName, {\r\n        from {height: 0; }\r\n        to { height: @sub-nav-heigth * @counter;}\r\n    });\r\n\r\n    .@{fadeOutUpName} {\r\n        animation-name: @fadeOutUpName;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .@{fadeInDownName} {\r\n        animation-name: @fadeInDownName;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .fadeLoop(( @counter + 1 ));\r\n}\r\n.fadeLoop(1);\r\n\r\n.animated {\r\n    animation-duration: .3s;\r\n    animation-fill-mode: both;\r\n    overflow: hidden;\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n补充说明: 上述中使用到了字符串函数(e), 字符串函数(e)用于对CSS的转义，与~\"value\"类似。它接受一个字符串作为参数，并原样返回内容（不含引号）。它可用于输出一些不合法的CSS语法，或者是使用LESS不能识别的属性。使用上述函数有效的解决了less中变量只能在classname上拼接的缺陷，能够生成有效的变量名。\r\n\r\n## 二、循环\r\n``` less\r\n@scenes: throw, pickup, mine;\r\n@scenes-length: length(@scenes);\r\n\r\n.loop(@index) when(@index <= @scenes-length) {\r\n     @scene: extract(@scenes, @index);\r\n\r\n     &.scene-image-@{scene} {\r\n         background-image: url('./images/bottle-button-@{scene}.png');\r\n     }\r\n\r\n     .loop(@index + 1);\r\n}\r\n\r\n.loop(1);\r\n```","closed_by":null,"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hankliu62/hankliu62.github.com/issues/9/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hankliu62/hankliu62.github.com/issues/9/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null},"menus":["## 一、循环动画函数","## 二、循环"]},"__N_SSG":true}